snippet.title: PALADINS Now on the Epic Games Store!
snippet.description:
Paladins is now available FREE on the Epic Games Store! Available for a limited time, redeem the FREE Epic Bundle featuring 4 free Champions, 4 free Champion Skins, and a free Diamond chest roll! 
Download Paladins here: https://www.epicgames.com/store/product/paladins

Unlock the Onyx Stallion mount, free and exclusive to our YouTube subscribers: https://www.paladins.com/community

Follow us for updates!
http://facebook.com/paladinsgame
http://twitter.com/paladinsgame

Enter a fantasy world of ancient technology in Paladins, a team-based shooter with strategy elements and deep character customization. Through a unique card system, players can amplify and augment a character’s core set of abilities to play exactly how they want to play.  Paladins is a free-to-play, class-based first person shooter from Hi-Rez Studios, currently available on PC, Mac, Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, and PlayStation 4. Learn more at www.paladins.com!
